nt","Claude authentication","Account/credentials access"],"confidence":1,"facts":["User is looking for their Claude code API key","User reports not being able to find it","This is a support/help inquiry rather than a technical task"],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwlfhqe_7ae627a8c828","importance":2,"narrative":"The user is asking for help locating their Claude API key, indicating they may not have received it, lost it, or don't know where to find it in their account/dashboard. This is a common onboarding or account management question that requires directing them to the appropriate documentation or account settings.","sessionId":"7058b98f-8167-4834-a075-52b0181a8140","subtitle":"User unable to locate their API key","timestamp":"2026-06-27T16:47:43.203Z","title":"User asking about Claude API key location","type":"conversation"},"obs_mqwlfvpr_1ee72fd73d52":{"concepts":["Shell environment configuration","API key management","Shell rc file hierarchy"],"confidence":1,"facts":["ANTHROPIC_API_KEY is defined in ~/.zshrc at line 18","API key is 108 characters long (typical for Claude API keys)","Key is currently exported and available in the active shell environment","No ANTHROPIC_API_KEY found in other shell rc files (~/.zprofile, ~/.bash_profile, ~/.bashrc, ~/.profile, ~/.zshenv)","Command output properly redacted sensitive key material"],"files":["~/.zshrc"],"id":"obs_mqwlfvpr_1ee72fd73d52","importance":6,"narrative":"The user verified that the ANTHROPIC_API_KEY has been successfully added to their ~/.zshrc configuration file and is actively exported in the current shell session. The key is 108 characters long and matches expected Claude API key format. No duplicate configurations exist in other shell initialization files, indicating a clean setup.","sessionId":"7058b98f-8167-4834-a075-52b0181a8140","subtitle":"Checked shell configuration and current environment for API key","timestamp":"2026-06-27T16:48:01.325Z","title":"Verified ANTHROPIC_API_KEY environment variable setup","t